Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.22,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}无论是操兵相戕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.22,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}もう戦に出るのも
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.18,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}还是颠沛流离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.18,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}逃げるのも
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.64,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}抑或是惶惶不可终日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.64,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}怯えるのも
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.06,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}都该于此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.06,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}終わりにしたい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.06,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.06,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}それは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.69,CN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}这是可耻而又怯懦之举吗
